001package io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.processor;
002
003import io.github.kale_ko.bjsl.elements.ParsedElement;
004import org.jetbrains.annotations.NotNull;
005import org.jetbrains.annotations.Nullable;
006
007/**
008 * A type processor for converting elements to objects and objects to elements
009 *
010 * @version 1.0.0
011 * @since 1.0.0
012 */
013public interface TypeProcessor {
014    /**
015     * Converts an Object into a {@link ParsedElement}
016     *
017     * @param object The object to convert
018     *
019     * @return A new {@link ParsedElement} representing the Object
020     *
021     * @since 1.0.0
022     */
023    public @NotNull ParsedElement toElement(@Nullable Object object);
024
025    /**
026     * Converts a {@link ParsedElement} into an Object
027     *
028     * @param element The element to convert
029     *
030     * @return A new Object representing the element
031     *
032     * @since 1.0.0
033     */
034    public @Nullable Object toObject(@NotNull ParsedElement element);
035}
